## Logo Handling Guidelines

### Directory Structure
- `original_logos_hq/` - **NEVER modify** these original files
- `app/src/main/res/drawable/logo_*.webp` - Processed finals

### Adding New Station Logos
1. **Find source**: Prioritize native PNG with transparency over SVG
   - Best: Official website assets, FreebieSupply, Brandfetch
   - Good: Wikimedia Commons native PNG files
   - Avoid: Wikimedia SVG-to-PNG auto-conversions (cause halos)

2. **Download original**: Save to `original_logos_hq/` as PNG
   - Use descriptive name: `logo_stationname.png`
   
3. **Convert to WEBP**: 
   - Only format conversion, NO background removal
   - Max 1000px, quality 90
   - Save to `app/src/main/res/drawable/logo_stationname.webp`

4. **Update code**: Add entry in `RadioStations.kt`

### Quality Checklist
- [ ] Text clearly legible
- [ ] No gray/white halos around edges
- [ ] Works on both light and dark backgrounds
- [ ] File size reasonable (10-150KB typical)
